(194, '77.44.224.102', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64; rv:67.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/67.0', 'http://aviation-horizons.domdomta.com/admin/blogs/edit-save/3', 'Update data Should you buy an aircraft or simply lease one? at Blog', '<table class=\"table table-striped\"><thead><tr><th>Key</th><th>Old Value</th><th>New Value</th></thead><tbody><tr><td>title_en</td><td>Buy an aircraft or lease two</td><td>Should you buy an aircraft or simply lease one?</td></tr><tr><td>title_ar</td><td>Buy an aircraft or lease two</td><td>Should you buy an aircraft or simply lease one?</td></tr><tr><td>brief_en</td><td>Buy an aircraft or lease two Buy an aircraft or lease two</td><td>Making the decision of whether you should own an aircraft or just lease one is not simply a matter of being able to afford to buy an aircraft or not. In fact, there are many times when a person or company has more than enough capital to buy an aircraft outright, but it is actually a more lucrative solution to lease one. If you still have any doubts, consider this: more than one-third of all aircraft operated by airlines are leased by the airlines themselves.</td></tr><tr><td>brief_ar</td><td>Buy an aircraft or lease two Buy an aircraft or lease two</td><td>Making the decision of whether you should own an aircraft or just lease one is not simply a matter of being able to afford to buy an aircraft or not. In fact, there are many times when a person or company has more than enough capital to buy an aircraft outright, but it is actually a more lucrative solution to lease one. If you still have any doubts, consider this: more than one-third of all aircraft operated by airlines are leased by the airlines themselves.</td></tr><tr><td>desc_en</td><td><h1><font face=\"Comic Sans MS\" color=\"#104A5A\">In <font color=\"#104A5A\">Fleet and Aviation  ? </font><br></font></h1><p><font face=\"Comic Sans MS\" color=\"#104A5A\">In <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Publishing\" title=\"Publishing\">publishing</a> and <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Graphic_design\" title=\"Graphic design\">graphic design</a>, <b>Lorem ipsum</b> is a <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Placeholder_text\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Placeholder text\">placeholder text</a> commonly used to demonstrate the visual form of a document without relying on meaningful content (also called <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Greeking\" title=\"Greeking\">greeking</a>).\r\n Replacing the actual content with placeholder text allows designers to \r\ndesign the form of the content before the content itself has been \r\nproduced.\r\n</font></p><p><font face=\"Comic Sans MS\" color=\"#104A5A\">The lorem ipsum text is typically a scrambled section of <i><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/De_finibus_bonorum_et_malorum\" title=\"De finibus bonorum et malorum\">De finibus bonorum et malorum</a></i>, a 1st-century BC Latin text by <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cicero\" title=\"Cicero\">Cicero</a>, with words altered, added, and removed to make it nonsensical, improper <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Latin\" title=\"Latin\">Latin</a>.\r\n</font></p><p><font face=\"Comic Sans MS\" color=\"#104A5A\">A variation of the ordinary lorem ipsum text has been used in <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Typesetting\" title=\"Typesetting\">typesetting</a> since the 1960s or earlier, when it was popularized by advertisements for <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Letraset\" title=\"Letraset\">Letraset</a> transfer sheets. It was introduced to the <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Information_Age\" title=\"Information Age\">information age</a> in the mid-1980s by <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aldus\" title=\"Aldus\">Aldus Corporation</a>, which employed it in graphics and word-processing templates for its desktop publishing program <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adobe_PageMaker\" title=\"Adobe PageMaker\">PageMaker</a>. Many popular <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Word_processor_(electronic_device)\" title=\"Word processor (electronic device)\">word processors</a> use this format as a placeholder. Some examples are <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pages_(word_processor)\" title=\"Pages (word processor)\">Pages</a> or <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Microsoft_Word\" title=\"Microsoft Word\">Microsoft Word</a>.\r\n</font></p><p><font face=\"Comic Sans MS\" color=\"#104A5A\">In <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Publishing\" title=\"Publishing\">publishing</a> and <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Graphic_design\" title=\"Graphic design\">graphic design</a>, <b>Lorem ipsum</b> is a <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Placeholder_text\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Placeholder text\">placeholder text</a> commonly used to demonstrate the visual form of a document without relying on meaningful content (also called <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Greeking\" title=\"Greeking\">greeking</a>).\r\n Replacing the actual content with placeholder text allows designers to \r\ndesign the form of the content before the content itself has been \r\nproduced.</font><br><br></p><p><font face=\"Comic Sans MS\" color=\"#104A5A\">The lorem ipsum text is typically a scrambled section of <i><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/De_finibus_bonorum_et_malorum\" title=\"De finibus bonorum et malorum\">De finibus bonorum et malorum</a></i>, a 1st-century BC Latin text by <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cicero\" title=\"Cicero\">Cicero</a>, with words altered, added, and removed to make it nonsensical, improper <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Latin\" title=\"Latin\">Latin</a>.\r\n</font></p><p><br></p><p><font face=\"Comic Sans MS\" color=\"#104A5A\">A variation of the ordinary lorem ipsum text has been used in <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Typesetting\" title=\"Typesetting\">typesetting</a> since the 1960s or earlier, when it was popularized by advertisements for <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Letraset\" title=\"Letraset\">Letraset</a> transfer sheets. It was introduced to the <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Information_Age\" title=\"Information Age\">information age</a> in the mid-1980s by <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aldus\" title=\"Aldus\">Aldus Corporation</a>, which employed it in graphics and word-processing templates for its desktop publishing program <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adobe_PageMaker\" title=\"Adobe PageMaker\">PageMaker</a>. Many popular <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Word_processor_(electronic_device)\" title=\"Word processor (electronic device)\">word processors</a> use this format as a placeholder. Some examples are <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pages_(word_processor)\" title=\"Pages (word processor)\">Pages</a> or <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Microsoft_Word\" title=\"Microsoft Word\">Microsoft Word</a>.\r\n</font></p><p><br></p></td><td><h1><font face=\"Comic Sans MS\" color=\"#104A5A\">In <font color=\"#104A5A\">Fleet and Aviation  ? </font><br></font></h1><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif;color:#030305;mso-ansi-language:\r\nEN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">However, buying a brand new aircraft may be an appealing prospect at\r\nfirst. But over time, the aircraft will likely depreciate in value. For\r\nairlines, in particular, this can be a problem when an upgrade becomes\r\nessential. For personal owners, this may not be as much of a problem.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif;color:#030305;mso-ansi-language:\r\nEN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">An airline that owns its own aircraft will also go a long way to\r\nreassuring its stockholders and customers because these assets naturally double\r\nup as substantial collateral. This opens the door to raise funds when needed.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif;color:#030305;mso-ansi-language:\r\nEN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">Because you own the aircraft, there is nothing to stop you modifying it\r\nto your liking. Whether that means upgraded engines, a unique outer design or\r\nbrand new interiors, you can custom design your aircraft just the way you like\r\nit. With a lease, this is much more difficult and would require the owner’s\r\npermission at the very least.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif;color:#030305;mso-ansi-language:\r\nEN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">When it comes to buying an aircraft, the aircraft will be yours to keep.\r\nThis means you have a tangible and valuable asset to show for your investment,\r\nand if the market becomes favorable to sellers there is the opportunity to turn\r\na profit – or at least a favorable return.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><h2 style=\"background:white\"><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#030305;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">What\r\nif I wanted to buy an aircraft?</span></b><span style=\"font-family:\r\n&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#030305;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></h2><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif;color:#030305;mso-ansi-language:\r\nEN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">Despite its upsides, leasing will typically cost more in the long term\r\nthan buying outright. Just like renting a house can be more affordable than\r\ntaking out a mortgage, but ultimately leave you with no assets to show for your\r\nmoney, so too does leasing have a rather unsatisfying conclusion.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif;color:#030305;mso-ansi-language:\r\nEN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">Finally, one huge advantage is that getting the most up-to-date aircraft\r\ndoesn’t have to be such a burden when leasing. When buying an aircraft, the\r\ncompany will begin to take on the burden of its age over time. To upgrade to a\r\nnewer model, a buyer would have to be found. When leasing, this is no longer an\r\nissue.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif;color:#030305;mso-ansi-language:\r\nEN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">The most business savvy minds out there will also be aware of the\r\nbenefits that leasing an aircraft can have on a company’s balance sheet.\r\nLeasing an aircraft does not qualify as either an asset or a liability. Shrewd\r\nbusinesses can use this to make the best of their key ratios.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif;color:#030305;mso-ansi-language:\r\nEN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">Even if a company can afford to buy an aircraft, it may well be\r\npreferable to lease it instead. There are a lot of different reasons for this.\r\nFor instance, retaining the money that would have been spent on the upfront\r\ncost of an aircraft frees up funds for other avenues of the business. This\r\ncould mean expanding the business more quickly and ergo driving more success.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif;color:#030305;mso-ansi-language:\r\nEN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">One of the main advantages of leasing an aircraft comes from one of the\r\nmost obvious and essential places – affordability. If a person or company can’t\r\nafford to raise enough money to purchase an aircraft outright, leasing one\r\nmeans they can begin to enjoy the benefits of aircraft ownership regardless.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><h2 style=\"background:white\"><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#030305;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">The\r\nAdvantages of Leasing an aircraft</span></b><span style=\"font-size:\r\n18.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#030305;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></h2><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif;color:#030305;mso-ansi-language:\r\nEN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">But wait! why would an airline with huge amounts of funds available\r\nchoose to lease an aircraft rather than buy one? There are in fact a multitude\r\nof reasons, for both cases.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif;color:#030305;mso-ansi-language:\r\nEN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">Making the decision of whether you should own an aircraft or just lease\r\none is not simply a matter of being able to afford to buy an aircraft or not.\r\nIn fact, there are many times when a person or company has more than enough\r\ncapital to buy an aircraft outright, but it is actually a more lucrative\r\nsolution to lease one. If you still have any doubts, consider this: more than\r\none-third of all aircraft operated by airlines are leased by the airlines\r\nthemselves.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:LatentStyles DefLockedState=\"false\" DefUnhideWhenUsed=\"false\"\r\n  DefSemiHidden=\"false\" DefQFormat=\"false\" DefPriority=\"99\"\r\n  LatentStyleCount=\"376\">\r\n  <w:LsdException Locked=\"false\" Priority=\"0\" QFormat=\"true\" Name=\"Normal\"></w:LsdException>\r\n  <