y;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif;color:#030305;mso-ansi-language:\r\nEN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">Ultimately, there is no definitive answer as to whether it’s better to\r\nlease an aircraft or buy an aircraft. The decision depends on the situation of\r\nthe individual or company. Even major airlines lease a significant percentage\r\nof aircraft, which shows that it isn’t a case of simply having the money\r\navailable – but spending it smartly. Aviation Horizons can help you make the\r\nright decision as whether to buy or lease an aircraft based on your capital as\r\nwell as future plans. Get in touch with us today and let us discuss what works\r\nbest for your advantage.</span></p><p><font face=\"Comic Sans MS\" color=\"#104A5A\"><br></font></p><p><br></p></td></tr></tbody></table>', 2, '2019-06-24 09:31:27', NULL);
