(481, '77.44.208.234', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/75.0.3770.100 Safari/537.36', 'http://aviation-horizons.domdomta.com/admin/about_us/edit-save/1', 'Update data  at about_us', '<table class=\"table table-striped\"><thead><tr><th>Key</th><th>Old Value</th><th>New Value</th></thead><tbody><tr><td>breif_en</td><td>Over a decade of experience Established in January 2007, Aviation Horizons is a trusted Saudi business jet operator company headquartered in Jeddah, Saudi Arabia. We are a fully licensed aircraft operator by the GACA (General Authority of Civil aviation) and the Ministry of Trade in Jeddah, KSA.</td><td>Established in January 2007, Aviation Horizons is a trusted Saudi business jet operator company headquartered in Jeddah, Saudi Arabia. We are a fully licensed aircraft operator by the GACA (General Authority of Civil aviation) and the Ministry of Trade in Jeddah, KSA.</td></tr><tr><td>breif_ar</td><td>Over a decade of experience Established in January 2007, Aviation Horizons is a trusted Saudi business jet operator company headquartered in Jeddah, Saudi Arabia. We are a fully licensed aircraft operator by the GACA (General Authority of Civil aviation) and the Ministry of Trade in Jeddah, KSA.</td><td>Established in January 2007, Aviation Horizons is a trusted Saudi business jet operator company headquartered in Jeddah, Saudi Arabia. We are a fully licensed aircraft operator by the GACA (General Authority of Civil aviation) and the Ministry of Trade in Jeddah, KSA.</td></tr><tr><td>description_en</td><td><p><span style=\"color: rgb(18, 65, 95); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\">At Aviation Horizons we genuinely value your time, making sure that boarding with us is always luxurious and seamless. Our aim is to deliver a tailored service to each and every one of our clients, getting them to their destinations fast, comfortably and safely without the stress and hassle normally associated with overcrowded commercial aircrafts.&nbsp;</span><br style=\"color: rgb(18, 65, 95); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(18, 65, 95); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\">Operating 24 hours a day, 365 days a year, our fleet serves thousands of local and international destinations across Europe and the Middle East. Whether your journey is regional or intercontinental, Aviation Horizons can fly you anywhere in the world, in a VVIP aircraft that best suits your needs.</span></p><h4 style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(18, 65, 95); margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 22px;\">Our Vision</h4><p style=\"font-size: 20px; color: rgb(18, 65, 95); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Our vision at Aviation Horizons is to lead corporate jet and VIP aircraft management operations in the Middle East and be the preferred aircraft operator partner and aviation services provider in the Saudi Arabia, Europe and the Middle East.</p><p style=\"font-size: 20px; color: rgb(18, 65, 95); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br></p><h4 style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(18, 65, 95); margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 22px;\">Our Mission</h4><p style=\"font-size: 20px; color: rgb(18, 65, 95); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Our mission is to provide our clients with the best, fully customized service in private aviation and corporate jets with the extraordinary care they deserve at a reasonable cost while safety, security and luxury remain uncompromised.</p><p style=\"font-size: 20px; color: rgb(18, 65, 95); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br></p><h4 style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(18, 65, 95); margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 22px;\">Our Values</h4><p style=\"font-size: 20px; color: rgb(18, 65, 95); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Our values define what we believe in and how we behave to deliver our mission and vision. Our dedicated employees have the highest levels of expertise and do their best to go above and beyond our clients’ expectations of a world-class aircraft operator company in the kingdom.&nbsp;<br>We are driven by our values to help our clients:</p><ul style=\"color: rgb(18, 65, 95); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><li style=\"font-size: 20px;\">Relax and unwind while enjoying and making the most of every moment of their flight.</li><li style=\"font-size: 20px;\">Experience the luxury of our timely on ground handling services, top-notch on-board services and elegant sky dining.</li><li style=\"font-size: 20px;\">Leave the worry associated with flying arrangements behind and reach their destinations on time.</li></ul><p style=\"font-size: 20px; color: rgb(18, 65, 95); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Being part of the Saudi nation, our key values and responsibilities towards our society are:</p><ul style=\"color: rgb(18, 65, 95); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><li style=\"font-size: 20px;\">Boosting profitability, efficiency and performance of the kingdom’s aviation sector under the Saudi vision for 2030.</li><li style=\"font-size: 20px;\">Simplifying processes and increasing passenger convenience while reducing costs and improving efficiency.</li><li style=\"font-size: 20px;\">Driving major airport developments across Saudi Arabia.</li></ul><h4 style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,